  "text": "Theorem 4.8 can be interpreted as Poincaré-Birkhoff-Witt theorem for the algebra R g,γ (W ). Theorems 4.7, 4.8 also have the following implication. (see [CITATION_1] ), and that all the remaining relations match as well.",
